      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the most exacting standards. This specimen represents a rare opportunity to acquire a motorcar in pristine, showroom condition. Every detail, from the flawless exterior finish to the immaculate cabin, reflects a history of uncompromising care and meticulous preservation. For the discerning buyer who accepts only the finest, this vehicle offers a peerless ownership experience.",
