    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative example of the E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit boasts a documented rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement, addressing the chassis's primary known weak points. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, channeling power through a fresh variable M-differential lock. The suspension utilizes factory-spec bushings and dampers, maintaining original kinematics and damping rates. The exterior finish is flawless, showing no orange peel or oxidation, while the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. This is a mechanically sorted, collector-grade machine for the purist who demands peak atmospheric performance.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
