    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is an exceptional example of a meticulously maintained vehicle that truly earns the title of 'showroom condition.' Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, the exterior is entirely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. It has been strictly garage-kept and never driven in inclement weather. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery shows no creasing or bolster wear, and the carpets have been protected by factory mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the high-fidelity sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It comes with a complete, binder-organized service history from a certified dealership, including a recent comprehensive inspection, fresh synthetic oil, and a full brake fluid flush. The tires have nearly full tread remaining, and the engine bay is spotless. If you are looking for a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like a brand-new car, this is it. Clean title in hand and ready for a discerning collector or enthusiast.",
